## IMPORTANT NOTICE

This package is an independent Flutter adaptation of the Siemens iX Design System.
It is NOT developed, maintained, or endorsed by Siemens AG or the Siemens Industrial 
Experience team.

### Siemens iX Design System Attribution

The design patterns, guidelines, and visual language this package implements are based
on the Siemens iX Design System (https://ix.siemens.io), which is owned and maintained
by Siemens AG.

Siemens iX is a registered trademark of Siemens AG. This package uses Siemens iX as a 
reference for design consistency but is not an official Siemens product.

### Icon Attribution

Icons in this package are sourced from the official `@siemens/ix-icons` npm package 
(https://www.npmjs.com/package/@siemens/ix-icons). The icon generator downloads 
icons from the official Siemens source to ensure licensing compliance.

Users of this package are responsible for ensuring compliance with Siemens iX 
Design System licensing terms when using the downloaded icons.

### License Compliance

When using this package:

1. **Widget Components**: Licensed under MIT (see above)

2. **Icon Files**: Downloaded from official Siemens source. Users must comply with 
   Siemens iX Design System terms for icon usage.

3. **Design System References**: The design patterns implemented are based on the 
   Siemens iX Design System. Refer to https://ix.siemens.io for official guidelines 
   and terms.

